{
  "texts": [
    "For the selected features, the results of the analysis has indicated that the best features for prediction are the learning behavior and activity features which outperform other feature categories.",
    "Finally, the educational prediction findings hopefully can serve as a strong foundation for administrators and instructors to observe student's academic performance and provide a suitable educational adaptation that can meet their needs to protect them from failure and prevent their dropout.",
    "To develop well-defined and more accurate prediction solutions, a wide range of research issues need to be further explored.",
    "This includes adapting hybrid models and proving their effectiveness in producing high accuracy predictions.",
    "Moreover, the application of continuous prediction throughout the course is required to ensure that students can complete it until the end."
  ]
}